<plot>This limited collectors' edition video compilation spans Chris Whitley's career over three decades. The collection includes never-before-seen interview and live footage of Whitley busking in NYC's Washington Square Park in the late 70's, his short journey into Euro-glamland in the mid 80's, three Dirt Floor (1998) video and tour gems and live footage from the Rocket House (2001) 2001 Summer Tour.</plot><url>http://localhost:8983/solr/movie.html?104736</url></doc>
